                       MOUSE CONTROLS
Move mouse to control elevators and ailerons                                  
                               
1. Press right button for yoke mode.                         
2. Down elevator = forward on the mouse                      
3. Up elevator = backwards mouse                             
4. Left bank = left mouse                                    
5. Right bank = right mouse                                                   
                                      
Drag mouse to control brakes and throttle                                      
                                   
1. More throttle hold left button down and move forward      
2. Left throttle hold left button down and move backwards    
3. Apply brakes hold left button down and move left          
4. Release brakes hold left button down and move right       
   (NOTE: brakes are only effective on the ground.)          

